<p>Your code is <span><%= @@code.join(", ") %></span>.</p>
<p>Here comes the computer's guess:</p>
<div id="sign"><p><%= guess %></p></div>
<div>
	<p>Please give your feedback about the computer's guess. Type 'B' for a correct color in a correct position. Type 'W' for a correct color in an incorrect position. Type '?' for an incorrect guess. For example: B, ?, W, B</p>
</div>
<form method="POST" action="/feedback" >
	<input type="text" name="feedback" />
	<input type="submit" value="Submit!" />
</form>